#. [unit_type], id=AE_ext_undead_Doom_Prophet, race=undead
#: .\units\EE_units\undead\b3-Doom_Prophet.cfg:5
msgid "Doom Prophet"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_ext_undead_Doom_Prophet, race=undead
#: .\units\EE_units\undead\b3-Doom_Prophet.cfg:35
msgid ""
"This unit art and code is from Undead Legion - War of Legends Era, redesigned"
" as custom unit by IPS to fit EE - Undead faction.\n"
"\n"
"At long last, necromantic practitioners have paid the ultimate sacrifice for "
"the dark arts into which they have delved, and have, themselves, entered into"
" undeath. At the apex of their power, they have become darkness liches, a "
"waking embodiment of dread. They have, beyond any doubt, passed the point of "
"no return, and their power and immortality will have to provide consolation "
"for what they have lost in their quest to achieve them."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_agl_steelhive_Sentinel, race=AE_agl_steelhive, gender=female
#: .\units\misc_units\steelhive\steel_astigmatic.cfg:4
msgid "Steel Sentinel"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_agl_steelhive_Sentinel, race=AE_agl_steelhive, gender=female
#: .\units\misc_units\steelhive\steel_astigmatic.cfg:18
msgid ""
"This unit art and code is from Steel Hive - War of Legends Era, redesigned as"
" custom unit by IPS to fit AE - Steelhive faction.\n"
"\t\n"
"Sentinel is a variant of Sparkgazer upgrade, which at being heavier they "
"don't fly as high as other Oculus models. Still, they can hold villages and "
"castle tiles with 60% terrain defense which is very valuable, but their extra"
" size makes them to suffer from 40% defense in most places. Sentinel will "
"also colide at close enemies dealing them impact damage type. This model is "
"more ressistant to impact damage type, but has no bonus heat ressistance."
msgstr ""

