#: .\units\misc_units\steelhive\steel_dreadnought.cfg:18
msgid ""
"This unit art and code is from Steel Hive - War of Legends Era, redesigned as"
" custom unit by IPS to fit AE - Steelhive faction.\n"
"\t\n"
"Dreadnought are siege master pieces and among finest of Steelhive Army. "
"They're capable to retaliate at melee and to fly brining havoc in a wide "
"area."
msgstr ""

