msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_agl_steelhive_Bombardier, race=AE_agl_steelhive, gender=female
#: .\units\misc_units\steelhive\steel_skewer.cfg:17
msgid ""
"This unit art and code is from Steel Hive - War of Legends Era, redesigned as"
" custom unit by IPS to fit AE - Steelhive faction.\n"
"\t\n"
"Bombardiers are more refined prototype of Rocketers, they can fire much "
"harder bombards againist their objectives and if not stopped at time the "
"destruction they can leave over enemy lines will be enormous."
msgstr ""

