#. [unit_type], id=AE_agl_steelhive_Avalanche, race=AE_agl_steelhive, gender=female
#: .\units\misc_units\steelhive\steel_syren.cfg:13
msgid ""
"This unit art and code is from Steel Hive - War of Legends Era, redesigned as"
" custom unit by IPS to fit AE - Steelhive faction.\n"
"\t\n"
"Avalanche is among finest and most elegant fighting models that steelhive has"
" to offer, it offers among best fighting performance as well it looks so "
"aesthetic when deployed. Now flies at low height which adds it better "
"movement costs and ground terrain defenses. Its blade shock enemies, while "
"dealing impact damage type because of short circuits."
msgstr ""

